
Attachments

(Get Request)
attachments/:account_id
-Gets All Attachments On The Account
    Get params
        account_id

(Post Request)
attachments/:account_id
-Sends File To BC And Returns A Attachment Token
    Attachment Tokens Are Used In Comments, Uploads, etc..
    Get Params
        account_id
    Post Params
        media_object ( file )

(Get Request)
attachments/:account_id/project/:project_id
-Gets All Attachments Of A Project
    Get params
        account_id
        project_id